==English==

===Etymology===
From {{compound|en|scare|crow}} from 1530s. Replaced original {{m|en|shewel}} from Middle English {{m|enm|sheweles}}, from an unattested Old English form composed of {{compound|ang|scȳn|-els}} ([[scīewels]]). Compare Middle Low German [[schūwelse]] and  Middle High German [[schiusel]]. More at {{m|en|shy}}.

